        "message": "Abandoned\n\nWrapper classes are prone to the same issues as Mapper classes (i.e., forgetting to include added fields in the conversion methods).  That being the case, there's no advantage to creating wrapper classes and, as they introduce another set of unneeded classes, why create the confusion?",
